parameters:
\n<Momo>Huh? Kino-chan, aren't you going to the after-
party?
\n<Kino>Hehehe... I have a commercial shoot after this☆
\n<Sawa>It's tough to be out this late...
\n<Kino>Being in charge of visuals is tough~...

\n<Momo>Pfft, even though I'm just leftovers in terms of
looks and body compared to Nene-chan (Neon),
right?

\n<Kino>Momo, you... I'm going to smack you on the head
with a slipper later.

\n<Sawa>Your true colors are showing... Be careful. And
Momo... It's not leftovers, it's a crushing
defeat...
\n<Kino>Pfft... As expected, I'm in charge of comedy♪

\n<Kino>Since you didn't compliment me... Cough, well
then, I'm off~☆

\n<Kino>Neon! Today was amazing too! Well then, see you
later~☆

\n<Sawa>I also have a magazine interview tomorrow morning,
so I'll pass on the after-party.
\n<Sawa>I'm sorry... I didn't mean it like that...
\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]]\AA[F] I know, Sawa worries too much.

\n<Sawa>\F[\V[2]]\AA[F] Okay... then, we'll excuse
ourselves first.

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]]\AA[F] Phew... I'm sorry, I'm causing you
to worry...

They were actively involved in various activities
besides their band activities. As for me... I only
take on jobs related to music.

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]]\AA[F] (No, that's not it... It's because
of my \r[, being selfish, that I'm turning down
everything.)

Minato Neon: (I suppose I should be more flexible.
But all I can do is sing, and I don't feel
confident in handling anything else.)

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]]\AA[F] (Why do I always get jobs like
gravure shoots or swimsuit CM shoots...)

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]]\AA[F] (...It's not my fault. It's
\N[5]-san who keeps bringing me these kinds of
jobs, yeah, yeah...)

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]]\AA[F] Hehe... How about I keep you
company until morning and vent my frustrations to
you...

With a mischievous spirit bubbling up ever so
slightly, \# briskly left the dressing room...

The next day, \N[5] brought a typewriter to
the band practice room.
